      <title>VSC, 비쥬얼 스튜디오 코드</title>
      <link>http://pictureyou-neo.github.io/2020/09/15/vsc-visual-studio-code/</link>
      <guid>http://pictureyou-neo.github.io/2020/09/15/vsc-visual-studio-code/</guid>
